OL,5,G1820 Four in a Bed
OL,6,     FIn the Scottish Highlands, things
OL,7,     Fget off on the wrong foot at
OL,8,     FStephen and Margaret's Clachan
OL,9,     FGarden B&B thanks to an unpopular
OL,10,     Fshoes-off policy.
OL,11,G1855 Four in a Bed
OL,12,     FGraham hosts the week's second
OL,13,     Fvisit at his Highland Premier
OL,14,     FGlamping Pods glampsite near
OL,15,     FInverness, where he hopes to
OL,16,     Finspire a spirit of adventure with
OL,17,     Fa search for the Loch Ness
OL,18,     FMonster.
