OL,5,G1925 Four in a Bed
OL,6,     FIn Perthshire, the B&Bers stay at
OL,7,     FCultybraggan Camp, a site used as
OL,8,     Fa prisoner of war camp in World
OL,9,     FWar II. They've done it up since
OL,10,     Fthen, of course...
OL,11,G1955 Four in a Bed
OL,12,     FDuring the week's final visit, to
OL,13,     FJames and Neil's Uplawmoor Hotel
OL,14,     Fnear Glasgow, the B&Bers try their
OL,15,     Fhands at curling. But some
OL,16,     Frelationships seem to be on thin
OL,17,     Fice.
