OL,5,G2030 Four in a Bed
OL,6,     FIt's been a topsy-turvy week with
OL,7,     Fsome B&Bers delighted with their
OL,8,     Fscores - and others not so much.
OL,9,     FAfter a little bit of a praise and
OL,10,     Fa lot of moaning, who'll win?
OL,11,G2100 The Emergency Ward
OL,12,     FDr Papson struggles to cut a glove
OL,13,     Ffrom an injured construction
OL,14,     Fworker's hand. Dr Halid examines
OL,15,     Fthe injuries of a driver who's
OL,16,     Fcrashed his lovingly restored car.
